    <item>
      <title>API tokens in Console… with API and Clever Tools tips</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/changelog/2025/06-05-api-tokens-console-tips/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//localhost:1313/changelog/2025/06-05-api-tokens-console-tips/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;With &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/changelog/2025/03-07-clever-tools-3.12/&#34; &gt;Clever Tools 3.12&lt;/a&gt;, we&amp;rsquo;ve introduced a new way to query Clever Cloud&amp;rsquo;s API, with &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/api/howto/#api-tokens&#34; &gt;the API bridge and API tokens&lt;/a&gt;. Starting today, you can create, edit and revoke API tokens directly &lt;a href=&#34;https://console.clever-cloud.com/users/me/api-tokens&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;from your Clever Cloud profile page&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;API tokens in the Clever Cloud Console&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;api-tokens-in-the-clever-cloud-console&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#api-tokens-in-the-clever-cloud-console&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This interface also shows the token name, description, public ID, creation and expiration date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To create an API token, you need to provide:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your current password&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your 2FA code if active (activate it &lt;a href=&#34;https://console.clever-cloud.com/users/me/authentication&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you created your Clever Cloud account through the GitHub integration, you&amp;rsquo;ll be asked to set a password first.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/images/changelog/console-api-tokens.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Manage API tokens in Clever Cloud Console&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Clever Tools and API tips in the Console&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;clever-tools-and-api-tips-in-the-console&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#clever-tools-and-api-tips-in-the-console&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This interface also introduces a new &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.clever-cloud.com/developers/clever-components&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Web Component&lt;/a&gt; to show Clever Tools commands and API requests related to the page you visit. In the coming weeks, we&amp;rsquo;ll add more of these tips over the Clever Cloud Console.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/images/changelog/console-api-tokens-tips.webp&#34; alt=&#34;API Tokens API &amp; Clever Tools Tips&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
